<br>
I'll agree with you regarding our medical care and education system, it is sorely lacking in many respects but that all depends on where you live. Some public schools and community hospitals are excellent, just depends on where you go. I've experienced your form of medical care run completely by the government and compared to what we have here, you can keep it.  I prefer to have the best technology,the best doctors and unlimited availability to equipment and we do have that here.<br>
<br>
<br>
